	Cruz crush    
	 London, Dec. 3 (PTI): Spanish actress Penelope Cruz says she just cant stop kissing veteran actress Meryl Streep whenever she meets her.       
	We only know each other from seeing each other at awards ceremonies or those kinds of events, but whenever I see her, I always go up to her and start kissing her, Cruz said in the latest issue of Interview magazine.       
	I dont even say anything, I just kiss her. She must think Im some crazy person, the 35-year-old actress said.     
	Son shock    
	 London (PTI): Actress Kate Hudsons five-year-old son Ryder was left in shock after he saw his mother filming in a sexy outfit on the sets of Nine. The 30-year-old actress was shooting a song-sequence for the musical on the day Ryder visited. He was stunned when he saw the skimpy dress his mother was wearing.                                                                                                                                                       
